Package: julianlme
Title: R Interface to JuliaNLME
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("InsightRX", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "dev@insightrx.com"))
Description: R wrapper around the JuliaNLME nonlinear mixed-effects modeling
    library. Provides functions to fit population PK/PD models and simulate
    from them, with the same model file format (.jnlme) and three estimation
    methods: FOCE/FOCE-I, SAEM, and ITS.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    JuliaCall (>= 0.17.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
